# ── embedded build dependency ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# amenan-ui is its OWN git repo (github.com/doumouya/amenan-ui), cloned here as a
# sibling build input. Ignore it so git doesn't add it as a broken gitlink. The
# deployable index.html files are committed, so the repo still serves without it.
# (Prefer to vendor it? Remove this line and add it as a submodule instead.)
/amenan-ui/

# ── dependencies & build outputs (regenerable; never commit) ──────────────────
**/node_modules/
**/target/
**/dist/
**/.build/
**/pkg/
**/pkg-web/
**/pkg-node/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/web/wasm/*.wasm
**/wasm/*_bg.wasm
# …but the front-door EMBEDS csv-workbench (portfolio/apps/csv-workbench) and self-hosts its
# Polars engine, so track that one deployed wasm binary (the build-side copies stay ignored above).
!portfolio/apps/csv-workbench/wasm/data_bg.wasm

# ── secrets / local env ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# ── firebase ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.firebase/
firebase-debug.log
*-debug.log

# ── logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ── OS / editor cruft ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
.idea/
